name: EnhancedDoubleHasher_indicesTest
description: Unit tests for the EnhancedDoubleHasher class, focusing on the indices method and related functionalities.

test_cases.name: testIndicesNonNullShape
test_cases.description: Tests that a NullPointerException is thrown when passing a null Shape to the indices method.

test_cases.name: testAsIndexArray
test_cases.description: Tests the asIndexArray method of IndexExtractor to ensure indices are within the valid range.

test_cases.name: testProcessIndicesNonNullConsumer
test_cases.description: Tests that a NullPointerException is thrown when passing a null IntPredicate to the processIndices method.

test_cases.name: testProcessIndicesValidConsumer
test_cases.description: Tests the processIndices method with a valid IntPredicate that ensures indices are within the valid range.

test_cases.name: testProcessIndicesInvalidConsumer
test_cases.description: Tests the processIndices method with an invalid IntPredicate that ensures indices are out of the valid range.

test_cases.name: testProcessIndicesWithKGreaterThanBits
test_cases.description: Tests the processIndices method with a Shape where K is greater than the number of bits.

test_cases.name: testProcessIndicesWithKLessThanBits
test_cases.description: Tests the processIndices method with a Shape where K is less than the number of bits.
